.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/122140/', '', 'Cyclosporine, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, More', 'Naltrexone, Oxymorphone, Pentazocine, Morphine, Butorphanol, Ibuprofen, Codeine, Nalbuphine, Acetaminophen, Tramadol, Dihydrocodeine, More', 1767369485);
