evelopment of tuberculosis in patients who tested negative for latent tuberculosis infection prior to initiating therapy.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/122164/', '', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, Thalidomide, More', 'Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, Emapalumab, Baricitinib, Tofacitinib, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab', 1767369485);
